verbose_text: To further validate the interaction between RBFOX3 and the hTERT promoter, we pulled down the nuclear proteins bound at the hTERT promoter in HCC cells using the 5 '-biotin labeled hTERT promoter probe and streptavidin-agarose beads, and detected RBFOX3 in the nuclear protein / DNA complex using the RBFOX3 specific antibody by Western blot.
evidence: interaction between RBFOX3 and the hTERT promoter
